INSTALLATION:

1. Unzip the folder 'magiczoom' from this archive to the 'modules/' directory of your PrestaShop store.

2. Activate the module through the 'Modules' menu in your PrestaShop administrative panel.

3. You've now installed Magic Zoom!

4. To setup your page, go to:

Admin > Modules > Magic Zoom

